items.name: Ksitigarbha Bodhisattva 地藏王菩萨
items.description:
Bio: 

Kṣitigarbha, a bodhisattva revered in East Asian Buddhism, is often depicted as a Buddhist monk. His name can be translated into various versions, such as "Earth Treasury," "Earth Store," "Earth Matrix," or "Earth Womb."

Bodhisattva Ksitigarbha took a great vow to guide all living beings from hell and refused to achieve Buddhahood until all hells were emptied.

This noble commitment has earned him the title of the bodhisattva of hell-beings. Moreover, in Japanese culture, he is regarded as the guardian of children and the patron deity of deceased children and aborted fetuses.

Typically portrayed as a serene monk with a halo encircling his shaved head, Kṣitigarbha carries a staff to forcibly open the gates of hell and a wish-fulfilling jewel that illuminates the darkness.

Link:

[Buddhist Manga] The Original Vows of Ksitigarbha Bodhisattva Sutra

[Video] The story of Kshitigarbha Bodhisattva Bright Eye Rescuing Her Mother

items.name: Futura Sienna
items.description:
My rating vs expectation: 90%

(Medium quality dataset. Likeness is good despite dataset. Training method could be improved.)

All TIs I make depict real adults. Please apply it with good judgement. If you're the model and want this removed reach out to me via link below. I welcome all criticisms and suggestions with curiosity. If you like my work, buy me a house:
https://ko-fi.com/futurafree

This TI was trained in sd1.5 base with 5 vectors, 23 images, 5000 steps, and 217 epochs. This was finetuned for epiCRealism evo3 and Realistic Vision V4.0, but may work on others.

TIPS:

  • MUST be the first word in the prompt for likeness and consistency.

    • Example: futurasienna5000v5, portrait of a woman, long dress etc.

    • Not: Portrait of futurasienna5000v5, etc.

    • Sample images were not done this way because I was an amateur.

  • Recommended strength:

    • (0.98-1.0)

  • Optional:

    • Negative: nose ring, lying on floor

  • I use adetailer for all images, with mediapipe_face_full, blank pos and neg, 1024x1024, inpaint mask blur: 20, inpaint noise strength: 0.45.

  • Again, prompt in adetailer is left blank most of the time; (*exception*: if Loras/Lycoris is used and has significant impact on the appearance of the model's face, copy paste pos prompt without Loras/Lycoris into adetailer).

  • Upscaler I use: 4x_NMKD-Siax_200k.

items.name: Poker card figure
items.description:
TRIGGER WARNING (or aesthetic advice): this model connects body parts to make poker cards, putting in a realistic models will result in bodies with severe deformations (I personnally think this is hilarious, I have seen most movies on this page https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Body_horror ). You can't post them here (considered graphic violence).

This Lora is experimental. See 'Centrosymmetry' in suggested resources, it looks better.

This makes figures that have (approximate) central symmetry, to use as figure for poker cards.

The recommended aspect ratio is 0.6 (this is approximately the aspect ratio on poker cards figures), so 460*768. You might get two figures if you use a square resolution.

Prompt:

  • no activation word

  • helper word: upside down, multiple views, white background, simple background

  • do not prompt for clothing items or body parts under the belt (feet, trousers, dress, legs, ...), it will break the symmetry

  • lora weight: 0.5 to get better drawing (but lots of bad cards), 1.0 to get lots of good symmetry (but blurry faces)

Additional Notes:

  • this was made by rotating the cards in OpenCV and correcting cards by hand (I'm not very good with GIMP so the data isn't top quality). This might require another round of generate/select/train.

  • dataset included

  • as you can see on the images (and on the 'CentroSymmetry' Lora), upside down faces are not very good. You can actually tell whether the generation is going to be good during the generation process, the upside down face must be drawn at the same time as the upper face (and not twice as blurry).

  • I'm stupid, the danbooru tag is rotational_symmetry, but it is mostly 'dual_persona', that is two opposite but related characters

  • added an example of a 'joker' prompt (no rotational symmetry)

items.name: Harakht
items.description:
This is a Hypernetwork based off of a character from an episode of Conan the Barbarian, called An Evil Wind in Kunark. He is based off of an obscure deity from the Stygian pantheon from the Conan the Barbarian novels. He is based loosely on Horus. Depending where you go or look, the name Harak is also shown to be spelled Harakt and Harakht. While known as a falcon or hawk God, the cartoon shows Harak as being a mix of an eagle, hawk, and perhaps even a vulture. Also, he is portrayed as a demon and not a God.

Important thing to know about this Lora: Keep the weight of the Lora at under 0.5. For example, the Lora would look like this <lora:Harakht -000014:0.5> with the numbers at the end changed. Also, I find that the best and most optimal results from from when the weight of the Lora is set at 0.35. Anything above a weight of 0.5 results in increasing levels of erratic looks. At or near 0.5, the images closely resemble the art and style of the animation of the cartoon it came from.

Also to note, when this Lora is used with the Hypernetwork I made, both work best with the Lora set at 0.35 and the Hypernetwork set at a weight from 0.35 to 0.65. When used together, the results resemble the look and art style of the original animation while also a much more cleaner and sophisticated look than if the Lora were used alone.

For the CFG Scale and Denosing Strength, I thus far used the default settings for the program when experimenting with the Lora.

The Lora can be made better for sure, yet I ask for patience on that due to the age of the computer I am using.

Anna Simón Marí (Mollet del Vallès, Barcelona, 9 August 1982) is a Spanish TV host. She has a degree in journalism.

On 17 January 2005, at the age of 22, she started featuring on TV channel TeleTaxi. After a brief stint in call TV programs, she appeared in the satirical news program Estas no son las noticias on Cuatro. She appeared in two afternoon magazines in TV3, Tvist and Divendres (2009-2010). In 2010 she became one of the hosts (along with Florentino Fernández and Dani Martínez) of the "silly" comedy program Tonterías las justas (Cuatro, 2010) as well as its spiritual sequel Otra movida (Neox, 2011).

She was in the sixth position of singers imitation contest Tu cara me suena in Antena 3 and in September 2012 she joined as a partner of El hormiguero in the same channel.

On 19 February 2013 she became the host of the comedy program Así nos va, along with Florentino Fernández on La Sexta until June 2013. She was also the host of the magic contest program Por arte de magia on Antena 3 from September to October 2013. Since 2014 she has appeared in the comedy program Zapeando on laSexta.

素材太难找，为了增加泛化性用了和0.1版本截然不同的训练方法，训练集素材超过一千张，与之相对应的是画风整体过拟合（不影响使用就算了），手部有崩坏属于正常现象，如果整体崩坏严重是大模型问题推荐换个模型试试。

模型权重推荐：0.7-0.9，采样器推荐Euler a，推荐使用高分辨修复，重绘幅度不宜过高，不然会把画风盖过去，个人使用参数为0.5。细节不够可以用增加细节的lora，c站能搜到，但是权重也别太高，肢体会崩。

如果感觉经常出与画风无关的图，拿应该是提示词不对，或者可以试试把dmwr/(rubbish/)放进负面提示词，这个属于增加泛化附带的缺点，我也在考虑如何优化。总之，1.0的内容就这些了，都看到这里了不给个五星返图吗，真的要掉小眼泪辣ORZ

v1.0:

This model is pretty volatile as the dataset of syoyo's current style is pretty small. Thus I was limited to 28 images.

Use a weight of 0.8-0.9. Many of the example images were made with a weight of 1.0 but SD struggles to upscale and fix the face for most of them.

⬇Read the info below to get the high quality images🙏 (click on show more)⬇

Version Change Log

V30: Comprehensive improvement with significant improvement in realism and generalization.

版本说明

所有已发布版本之间并无明显的改善关系，各版本都各有优缺点，请根据自己的需求与喜好选择。

V29：自然圆润脸身体比例更协调，画面质感更真实

Introduction / 简介

Most realistic models aim to enhance film grain and blur to achieve a realistic photo effect, but images turning yellow and blurry. The ultimate goal of this model is to maintain high quality while maintaining authenticity.

One of the reasons for creating this model was my desire to have a foundational model that combines aesthetics with realism. I noticed that most models tend to fall into two extremes: some are realistic but lack artistic appeal, while others have beautiful visuals but lack realism. Thus, I developed this model, which, in my opinion, strikes a balance between aesthetics and realism, while being rooted in Eastern aesthetics.

Another reason behind creating this model was to have a highly compatible foundational model. Many existing models tend to be heavily biased towards specific styles, whereas I wanted a model that is truly versatile, allowing me to seamlessly transition between various styles, while relying on the diverse capabilities of the Lora community.

The model only needs to use a simple keyword to draw realistic photos, the whole body image has been greatly improved.

The model purposely reduces the skin blemishes of the young female characters. If you need to create a true sense of blemish, please emphasize it in the prompts.

If you think the model is good, don't forget to give it a five-star rating. Your support is the motivation for me to share.

大部分写实勒模型都是在增强胶片感与模糊来取得类似现实照片的效果，这导致图片往往发黄模糊，而这个模型的最终目标是高质量的同时保持真实性。

做这个模型的一个原因在于我想要一个兼具美学与真实感的基础模型，但大部分模型都是在走两个极端：一部分写实但欠缺美感，另一部分画面唯美但却不够写实。所以，我制作了这个个人认为平衡了美感与真实感的模型，当然这是基于东方审美的基础上。

另外一个原因则是，我想要一个兼容性极强基础模型，但大部分模型都特别偏向于某一风格，而我希望这个模型真的足够基础，让我可以很好的变换各种风格，而其他工作交给社区里种类繁多的Lora。

本模型只需要使用简单的关键词就可以绘出逼真的写实照片，对全身图像进行了大量改进。

模型特意减少了年轻女性人物皮肤瑕疵，如果需要营造真实的瑕疵感请在提示词中强调。

觉得模型不错的话，别忘了给个五星好评~ 你们的支持才是我分享的动力。

About VAE / 关于VAE:

The model is built-in Vae. The light, shadow and color effects are soft. If you like higher contrast images, you can switch directly to VAE or download the non-VAE version to use any VAE you like, or use the followingg: sd-vae-ft-mse-original.

Tips:

  • CLIP Skip：1 or 2 （Choosing 1 leads to results that are more aligned with the prompt and are more accurate. Choosing 2 yields more creativity and can also help reduce overfitting, depending on your preferences and needs.）

  • You can directly produce images with resolutions of 512*768, or higher, and then Hires Fix.

  • Orange Color : higher weight ≈ High Saturation & high contrasty

  • Option way to less contrasty: To make the image less contrasty you can use LoRA [Detail Tweaker LoRA] in a negative value.

  • CFG Scale( lower = real): 5 ~11

  • When used the CFG Scale Fix plugin, you will achieve astonishing images. Please search for usage instructions on your own.

  • Sampler reconmmend: DPM++ SDE Karras / DPM++ 2M SDE Karras / DPM++ 2M Karras

The trigger is diaper_under_tights and you can prompt for a limited selection of colours (white, black, nude, pink). I recommend running it about 0.9 LORA strength, but adjust to fit your needs. You can also prompt for "front" or "back" if you are struggling to get the figure to face the right way. This version is a bit better, but it still favours drawing ladies from behind.

You cannot prompt for lifted skirts in this version. It sometimes will draw that anyway, because there were some pictures like that in the training data, but you can't really make it happen on purpose. That will be improved in future if/when I can get a bigger and more diverse dataset.

This version seems to have a preference for chubby ladies, but you can prompt for "slim" if that's not to your taste. It also works fine with most prompting for outfits and scenery.

items.name: 背景及距离控制/background & distence control/背景と距離制御
items.description:
权重设置为负值让背景更深邃，人物镜头离得更远，使背景更具有规则化；

权重设置为正值让背景变简单，人物离镜头更近；使背景减少规则化；

镜头/距离的效果需要人物词和背景词占比不均匀时才容易触发，lora会加大这种不均衡，

假如写了非常多关于人物的词，而只有很少的背景词，而把人物维持高清拉远.现在可以办到了，用的另一个lora《边缘弱化/强化》，取负值，详见人群的图例。

使背景变得层次丰富或者简单的效果则没有限制。 无触发词，直接加载即可。推荐值-2~+2，对画面几乎没有污染-3，+3的值也可以使用，请自行尝试。

用法1：加非常多的背景词，并强调了人物词的权重。平衡人物词和背景词的占比。使得人物拥有足够多的像素，同时增加了背景丰富度和细节，使用-2的权重。

用法2：在画建筑、或者教室、超市货架等场景的时候使用负的权重，可以使背景更具规则，详见图例4，超市货架的例图。

用法3：想要突出主体、不想背景喧宾夺主的时候，可以设置正的权重，扁平化背景。正的权重也有非常细微的平滑线条的作用，适用于简单卡通形象的创作。

和lora 《背景细节增强/简化》一起使用将会得到令人惊异的效果，详见图例5和图例6

Setting the weight to a negative value makes the background deeper with more ditails and make the character farther to the viewer;

Setting the weight to the proof value makes the background simpler with less ditails and make the character closer to the viewer;

The effect of the lens/distence should be triggered when the proportion of character words and background words is unbalanced, and Lora will increase this imbalance.

If you write a lot of words about characters and only use little background words. Now you can maintain high definition and distance the characters, you can use another Lora called Edge weaken/strengthen', which takes a negative value, effect as shown in the legend of the crowd of girls.

The effect of making the background deeper or simpler is always work.

No trigger words, just set it directly. The recommended value is -2~+2.

Because this lora has almost no pollution to the picture, so a value of -3 and+3 can also be used. Please try it by yourself.

Usage1: Add a lot of background words and emphasize the weight of character words. Balanced the proportion of character words and background words. Make the characters have enough pixels while increasing background richness and detail, using -2 weight.

Usage 2: When drawing background, such as buildings, classrooms, or supermarket shelves, using negative weights can make the background more regular. Please refer to sample 4, an example of supermarket shelves.

Usage 3: When you want to highlight the subject and not want the background to dominate, you can set a positive weight to flatten the background. Positive weights also have a very slightly effect on smoothing lines, more suitable for creating simple cartoon characters.

Using it in conjunction with Lora<Background Detail Enhancement/Simplification> will achieve amazing results, as detailed in sample 5 and 6

重みを負の値に設定すると、背景がより深くなり、人物がより遠くになります。

重みを正の値に設定すると、背景がより簡単になり、人物がより近くになります。

レンズ/距離の効果は、人物提示語と背景提示語の比率が不均衡であることが必要とされ、このloraはその不均衡を大きくする。

もし人物に関する言葉が非常に多く書かれていて、背景語が少ないだけで、人物をハイビジョンに維持することができるようになったら、もう一つのlora『エッジ弱体化/強化』を使って、マイナス値を取って、女の子の群れの図例を詳しく見てください。

背景を豊かにしたり、簡単にしたりする効果には制限はありません。キーワードはありません、直接使用すればいいです。推奨値-2 ~+2は、画面には、ほとんど汚染されませんのて、-3、+3の値も使用できます、自分で試してみてください。

使い方1：非常に多くの背景語を加え、人物語の重みを強調した。人物語と背景語の比率をバランスさせた。人物に十分なピクセルを持たせながら、背景の豊かさとディテールを増やし、-2の重みを使用します。

使い方2：建築、あるいは教室、スーパーの棚などのシーンを描く時に、負の重みを使用して、背景をもっと規則的にすることができます、詳しくは図例4、スーパーの棚の例図を参照してください。

使い方3：本体を強調したいとき、背景が主客転倒したくないとき、正の重みを設定し、背景を平坦化することができます。正の重みはほんの少しけと、線を滑らかにすることができます、簡単なキャラクターの創作に適しています。

lora『背景詳細の強化/簡略化』と一緒に使用すると，凄まじい効果が得られる。詳細は図例5と図例6を参照

可以访问ritansonoac554的lora《背景细节增强/简化》链接

to accuss ritansonoac554‘s lora <Background Detail Enhancement/Simplification>

ritansonoac 554さんのlora『背景詳細の拡張/簡略化』リンクにアクセスできます

items.name: LahMix Mysterious
items.description:
